Project Structure:
bin - Contains resources created when building the project
doc - Contains source code documentation
guides - Contains guides for installing the MAR library and running Lighthouse
papers - Contains white papers written on the MAR library
res - Contains resources used by the Lighthouse application
src - Contains the source code for the MAR library and Lighthouse
Doxyfile - Used to created Doxygen documentation
Makefile - Used to build the project 
LICENSE - The license this project is released under
CREDITS - Contains credits for the project

Makefile:
mar - Builds the MAR library
install - Builds the MAR library and installs it
lighthouse - Builds the Lighthouse application
test - Builds the Lighthouse application and runs it
documentation - Builds source code documentation
uninstall - Uninstalles the MAR library
clean - Cleans the project
